{"links": {"self": {"href": "data/repositories/osrf/gazebo/pullrequests/2394/comments/21276329.json"}, "code": {"href": "https://api.bitbucket.org/2.0/repositories/osrf/gazebo/diff/osrf/gazebo:None..None?path=plugins%2FBlinkVisualPlugin.cc"}, "html": {"href": "#!/osrf/gazebo/pull-requests/2394/_/diff#comment-21276329"}}, "parent": {"id": 21227535, "links": {"self": {"href": "data/repositories/osrf/gazebo/pullrequests/2394/comments/21227535.json"}, "html": {"href": "#!/osrf/gazebo/pull-requests/2394/_/diff#comment-21227535"}}}, "deleted": false, "pullrequest": {"type": "pullrequest", "id": 2394, "links": {"self": {"href": "data/repositories/osrf/gazebo/pullrequests/2394.json"}, "html": {"href": "#!/osrf/gazebo/pull-requests/2394"}}, "title": "Visual plugin example: blink"}, "content": {"raw": "Resetting time shouldn't break the plugin anymore: 47ee845\n\nBut I noticed that even though visual plugins have a `Reset` function, that is never called. I ticketed issue #2012. It's a bit tricky because since VisualPlugins are on the client side, we can't connect to `event::Events::timeReset` for example. I think visuals would need to subscribe to `~/world_control`.", "markup": "markdown", "html": "<p>Resetting time shouldn't break the plugin anymore: <a href=\"#!/osrf/gazebo/commits/47ee845\" rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"ap-connect-link\">47ee845</a></p>\n<p>But I noticed that even though visual plugins have a <code>Reset</code> function, that is never called. I ticketed issue <a href=\"#!/osrf/gazebo/issues/2012/reset-is-never-called-for-some-plugin\" rel=\"nofollow\" title=\"Reset is never called for some plugin types\" class=\"ap-connect-link\">#2012</a>. It's a bit tricky because since VisualPlugins are on the client side, we can't connect to <code>event::Events::timeReset</code> for example. I think visuals would need to subscribe to <code>~/world_control</code>.</p>", "type": "rendered"}, "created_on": "2016-07-20T17:23:26.601042+00:00", "user": {"display_name": "Louise Poubel", "uuid": "{5cfa2075-477b-4ded-bdb9-8d2479544ec4}", "links": {"self": {"href": "https://api.bitbucket.org/2.0/users/%7B5cfa2075-477b-4ded-bdb9-8d2479544ec4%7D"}, "html": {"href": "https://bitbucket.org/%7B5cfa2075-477b-4ded-bdb9-8d2479544ec4%7D/"}, "avatar": {"href": "https://avatar-management--avatars.us-west-2.prod.public.atl-paas.net/557058:6ff86fcb-b7ab-44a5-b8a6-f6d9cae8b6e8/7d903d90-c5ea-4182-b7ef-0d467e9e1c74/128"}}, "nickname": "chapulina", "type": "user", "account_id": "557058:6ff86fcb-b7ab-44a5-b8a6-f6d9cae8b6e8"}, "inline": {"to": null, "from": null, "outdated": false, "path": "plugins/BlinkVisualPlugin.cc"}, "updated_on": "2016-07-20T17:23:26.607557+00:00", "type": "pullrequest_comment", "id": 21276329}